OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fwith some late evening brightness at
OL,7,Ffirst, before low cloud gradually
OL,8,Fspreads south through the evening and
OL,9,Fovernight bringing some patchy light
OL,10,Frain or drizzle at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be a largely cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning with some outbreaks of light
OL,14,Frain and drizzle. Drier through the
OL,15,Fafternoon with some brighter spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Freshening northeast
OL,17,Fwinds. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
