OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCool
OL,6,Fand quite cloudy on Sunday, but some
OL,7,Fbright spells at times. Early rain on
OL,8,FMonday followed by showers continuing
OL,9,Fthrough Tuesday, these heavy and
OL,10,Fblustery at times. Turning colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
